            array(
                'id' => 12,
                'title' => '5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件',
                'content' => '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">本文给大家安利5款个人使用过还不错的海外听歌的音乐应用软件，他们分别是Spotify，豆瓣，酷狗&amp;酷我，QQ音乐（配合代理），网易云音乐（配合代理）。排名仅作个人判断，供参考。</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 25px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; clear: both; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 17px; color: rgb(21, 123, 220); font-weight: normal; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">TOP5 Spotify</span></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Spotify</strong>是全球最大的正版流媒体音乐服务平台，2008年10月在瑞典首都斯德哥尔摩正式上线。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这个比较适合付费用户使用了，<strong>优点</strong>是正版音乐版权，可以在线收听，有手机APP应用和PC端的软件。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Spotify提供的服务分为免费和付费两种，免费用户在使用Spotify的服务时将被插播一定的广告。而付费用户则没有广告，且可以拥有更好的音质，在移动设备上使用时也可以拥有所有的功能。截止到2015年1月，Spotify已经拥有超过6000万的用户，其中1500万为付费用户。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">所以<strong>缺点</strong>也很明显，就是下载需要付费，而且针对国外音乐的Spotify，国内的华语歌也不是很全。</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 25px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; clear: both; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 17px; color: rgb(21, 123, 220); font-weight: normal; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">TOP4 豆瓣FM</span></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/0XsdrlG.png\" title=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(66, 158, 232); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"/uploads/image/1495612893706151.gif\" alt=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" title=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" width=\"320\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">豆瓣FM不仅可以找歌，更多的是提供一个FM电台。会根据个人的口味去搜索并自动播放你喜欢的音乐。用户可以通过加红心和删除垃圾操作来不断让FM程序符合自己的口味。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">通过长时间的「调教」可以让豆瓣FM更懂你。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">优点是：有手机APP，也支持PC在线听歌，多设备通过豆瓣账户同步。华语歌挺多，也均有正版版权。充满文艺的风格。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">缺点：曲库不算很全。</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 25px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; clear: both; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 17px; color: rgb(21, 123, 220); font-weight: normal; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">TOP3 酷狗 酷我音乐</span></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/mZuqTCO.png\" title=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(66, 158, 232); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"/uploads/image/1495612893706151.gif\" alt=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" title=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" width=\"540\" height=\"300\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">酷狗和酷我最大的优点就是对版权不是那么严查，很多盗版的歌也可以在线听。超大中文华语曲库，拥有国外版权，支持APP应用，也有电脑软件客户端，内置K歌插件。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">虽然逼格不是很高，但是依然进入了TOP 3。毕竟人在国外温饱比逼格重要。</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 25px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; clear: both; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 17px; color: rgb(21, 123, 220); font-weight: normal; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">TOP2 QQ音乐</span></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5ZGO8f5.png\" title=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(66, 158, 232); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"/uploads/image/1495612893706151.gif\" alt=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" title=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">国内的巨头腾讯旗下的音乐软件，在部分海外国家可以正常使用。腾讯财大气粗，每年都花大价钱去购买独家版权。海外的音乐也全。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">有手机APP，也有电脑端应用。UI设计上，腾讯也不是以前的腾讯了，可以说这款QQ音乐的界面比国外的Spotify还要好，没有理由不使用QQ音乐。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">缺点，部分海外地区不可以播放。不过没关系，请阅读破解海外版权的方案：</span><a title=\"海外破解网易云音乐和QQ音乐的版权限制\" href=\"https://www.seavia.com/share/oversea-163-cloud-music-qq-music.html\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(66, 158, 232); text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">海外破解网易云音乐和QQ音乐的版权限制</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">。</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 25px; padding: 5px 0px 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; clear: both; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 17px; color: rgb(21, 123, 220); font-weight: normal; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">TOP1 网易云音乐</span></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">写了这么多推荐网易的文章，丁磊是不是要打赏我，海外听歌TOP1，网易云音乐。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a title=\"海外翻墙回国享受大陆资源（音乐，电影，电视剧，动漫）\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3zR6oR4.jpg\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(66, 158, 232); text-decoration-line: none;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"海外翻墙回国享受大陆资源（音乐，电影，电视剧，动漫）\" src=\"/uploads/image/1495612893706151.gif\" alt=\"5款手机上最好用的国外听歌APP应用软件\" width=\"440\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这款软件我从去年网易云音乐还没有火的时候就一直在用了。无论是逼格（对于我，这种逼格已经够了），还是歌曲数目都是很充裕的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">我有个俄罗斯的朋友平时一直在iTunes上买音乐，我给他推荐了网易云音乐。虽然网易没有英文界面，但是俄罗斯朋友表示没有关系，他暗暗的记下了各个功能怎么点之后就抛弃了iTunes。后来这位朋友告诉我，很多俄语的歌网易云音乐都可以找到，如果这款软件有English interface指不定老外都会从spotify那边跑过来。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">网易云音乐有安卓版，windows版，ios版，mac版，iWatch版所以无论在什么设备和平台网易云音乐都是绝对好用的~~~注意，部分地区比如美国还是不支持海外版权，需要破解一下版权喔！！请阅读破解海外版权的方案：</span><a title=\"海外破解网易云音乐和QQ音乐的版权限制\" href=\"http://www.seavia.com/share/oversea-163-cloud-music-qq-music.html\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(66, 158, 232); text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">海外破解网易云音乐和QQ音乐的版权限制</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(63, 77, 84); line-height: 2.3em; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14.5px; font-family: Providence, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">破解完版权的网易云，可能是世界上最好用的音乐软件了。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">转自：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 104, 115); font-family: Providence, &quot